title: Rodgers other weapon will be _____? NFC North camp battles (Football 7/25)
description:
Will Brinson, Ryan Wilson and John Breech break down the NFL news of the day, including the Packers cutting Mike Daniels (3:00), Jalen Ramsey's training camp arrival (7:45), Mason Foster being released (13:00) and the Cowboys cutting Allen Hurns (17:45). Then they break down camp battles for the Packers (21:30), Bears (25:45), Vikings (30:00) and Lions (32:00).
